cal employee connect - the state controller's office employee self service portal - allows employees to view their paycheck information as well as download w-2s and other documents. employees may register for access to the system from any location and use personal email addresses if desired. for assistance with registration, please see the cal employee connect user guide [pdf] . agency code "260" and a recent pay statement will be needed to complete registration. if you do not have a recent pay statement, please contact your payroll representative for assistance. please note, you can find a tile for the portal on one.sjsu (search: sco portal). we recommend making that a favorite. university-personnel@sjsu.edu up north: 408-924-2450 up south: 408-924-2250  up webmaster up north administration building 242 up south upd building 3rd floor 